<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:14:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国7月工厂活动萎缩，服务业增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一份官方工厂调查显示，中国7月份制造业活动连续第三个月萎缩，这使得人们对北京将需要推出更多刺激措施的预期依然存在，因为旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累了经济增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-july-factory-activity-shrinks-services-grow-more-slowly-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国7月非制造业活动扩张放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-july-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一份官方工厂调查显示，中国7月份非制造业活动扩张放缓，这表明国内服务需求放缓，并加剧了房地产行业长达数年的危机的严重程度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:44:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-july-non-manufacturing-activity-expands-slower-pace-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>7月份中国制造业活动延续跌势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-manufacturing-activity-extends-decline-july-2024-07-31/</link><description>周三的一份官方工厂调查显示，中国7月份制造业活动连续第三个月萎缩，这增强了人们对北京将需要推出更多刺激措施的预期，因为旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累了经济增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-manufacturing-activity-extends-decline-july-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>中方就中美会晤言论向日方提出抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-official-protests-japans-negative-remarks-meeting-with-us-chinese-foreign-2024-07-31/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，北京已就日美会晤期间发表的涉华负面言论向东京表达不满。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-official-protests-japans-negative-remarks-meeting-with-us-chinese-foreign-2024-07-31/</guid></item><item><title>力拓对大量铜采购持开放态度，但对市场过热持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</link><description>力拓首席执行官雅各布·施陶霍姆(Jakob Stausholm)周三在讨论上半年业绩时表示，力拓可能会考虑进行大规模收购，但它必须提供在火热的铜市场中很难找到的价值。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:13:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/rio-tinto-reports-largely-flat-first-half-profit-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪探索进入加拿大汽车市场-监管备案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</link><description>根据本月早些时候提交的一份监管文件，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪正在寻求进入加拿大汽车市场，尽管加拿大官员正在考虑对从中国进口的汽车征收关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-explores-canadian-auto-market-entry-regulatory-filing-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国和美国的拖拉销售，星巴克效率提高提振利润</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-quarterly-global-sales-drop-larger-than-expected-china-weakness-2024-07-30/</link><description>星巴克门店运营的改善帮助​​这家咖啡连锁店满足了华尔街对季度利润的预期，尽管其全球销售额因美国和中国等主要市场消费者支出持续疲软而下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-quarterly-global-sales-drop-larger-than-expected-china-weakness-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官预计印度与乌克兰有更多接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二在参议院听证会上回答有关印度总理莫迪本月访问莫斯科的问题时表示，他预计很快就会有消息称印度正在加强与乌克兰的接触。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-中国金牌得主王的喜悦因狗仔队拍球事故而中断</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-gold-medalist-wangs-joy-cut-short-by-paparazzi-paddle-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，中国24岁的乒乓球运动员王楚钦与队友孙颖莎一起夺得了自己的第一枚奥运会金牌，他欣喜若狂。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-china-gold-medalist-wangs-joy-cut-short-by-paparazzi-paddle-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅二季度销量上升但中国市场低迷承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</link><description>法国化妆品巨头欧莱雅公布第二季度销售额增长 5.3%，低于预期，这可能进一步令本已担心重要的中国市场缺乏反弹的投资者感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>二号外交官表示，美国必须采取更多措施反击中国的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，华盛顿必须采取更多措施来对抗中国的行动，包括其建立军事基地的战略以及在非洲开采稀土矿的战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国马拉松选手准备在巴黎与职业选手并肩作战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marathon-chinese-runner-ready-deliver-alongside-pros-paris-2024-07-30/</link><description>栾玉帅每天要花12个小时送包裹。之后，他穿上运动鞋，开始一天中他最喜欢的部分——马拉松训练。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/marathon-chinese-runner-ready-deliver-alongside-pros-paris-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>更多历史性的中国药检呈阳性给巴黎游泳运动蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，《纽约时报》报道称，两名 2022 年游泳运动员的违禁类固醇检测结果呈阳性，但由于结果被归咎于受污染的食品，他们的临时禁赛被解除，中国因此再次陷入兴奋剂关注的焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国帮助意大利布雷博克服汽车行业的疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-posts-stable-margins-tough-market-shares-rise-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利高级制动器制造商布雷博周二公布，上半年核心盈利和收入温和增长，其亚洲市场及其业务有助于维护老旧车辆，帮助应对汽车行业黯淡的前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-posts-stable-margins-tough-market-shares-rise-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>对默克公司加德西在中国销售的担忧导致股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-second-quarter-tops-street-view-strong-keytruda-sales-2024-07-30/</link><description>默克公司周二表示，第二季度其Gardasil疫苗在重要的中国市场的出货量下降，引发投资者担忧，其股价暴跌逾9%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-second-quarter-tops-street-view-strong-keytruda-sales-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>